  "doc_id": "25704",
  "text": "Analysis of viral transcripts. The EToV (Berne isolate) genome sequence was confirmed by de novo assembly of unmapped and vRNA reads from the infected RNA-seq samples. Assembly was performed using Trinity (65) with the default settings for stranded single-ended (-SS_lib type \"F\") data. Viral contigs were identified using BLASTN (29) against a database of EToV reference sequences based on the NCBI records listed above. The viral contig was aligned to the reference using the MAFFT L-INS-i method [CITATION_1] .",
